                "Ti backing. Two samples 27.6 ug and 32.4 ug.",
                "Covered with Ni foils of 0.25 um thickness to prevent",
                "the material sputtering.",
                "The energy loss of fragments",
                "~8.5 MeV ,68% in Ni foil, 32% in 1st sample;",
                "~9.7 MeV, 64% in Ni foil, 36% in 2nd sample."
              ]
